         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">My dear Sir ¶  ¶ I ¶  ¶ have been requested to ask if you would oblige the Leichhardt Search Committee by intimating to the Chief Secretary the hope entertained, that the grant voted by the Legislativ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">M65.12.12</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Eliza Bromby to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>John Moore</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">M65/11597, unit 209, VPRS 3991/P inwards registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Office, Public Record Office, Victoria.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Enclosed with the above letter is a contingencies form made out to Mrs Jane Cutts, Honorary Treasurer of the Ladies' Leichardt Search Committee, 13 December 1865, for the Government's grant in aid of the Ladies Leichhardt Search Expedition of £500.</p>
               </note>My dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>have been requested to ask if you would oblige the Leichhardt Search Committee by intimating to the Chief Secretary the hope entertained, that the grant voted by the Legislative Assembly in aid of their enterprise may be paid to their account at the London Chartered Bank as soon as possible. As the year is drawing to a close, the Committee would avoid the difficulty that might arise in obtaining the sum, were the payment longer delayed. I trust you will excuse me for giving you this trouble.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The Chief Secretary, James McCulloch, annotated the file on [18] December 1865: 'Approved of above [action] and complied with'. There is also a note in another hand: 'Letter to Mrs Bromby 27th Decr /65'.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Believe me</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>My dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Yours truly</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Eliza S. Bromby</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">President of the Committee</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The Grammar School<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>i.e. Melbourne Grammar School.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Decr 12th</p>
